{"tid":2077665,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[高爾夫生還者2] 巴哈編輯比我鞭屍鞭到龜縮，要編輯部主管出黎道歉","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:36:07.000Z","uid":75050,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f38f7be01071bc335ddbeafb80e13a9bf4c807fd","tid":2077665,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"巴哈鞭屍post (內含豪哥奶狗廠原文) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=21876&amp;snA=2510&amp;tnum=83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D21876%26snA%3D2510%26tnum%3D83&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=6daff23e\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=21876&amp;snA=2510&amp;tnum=83</a><br />\n<br />\n事源，6月16日(即遊戲發售前三日)巴哈編輯阿豪係巴哈發左篇垃圾叫「《最後生還者 二部曲》巴哈姆特電玩瘋編輯全破無劇透感想 遊戲史上最高傑作」，內文奶隻game奶到不堪<br />\n<br />\n結果遊戲發售當日風向大變，而阿豪就開始潛水，連呢篇文都刪埋，但係比我發現條友居然將呢篇垃圾放左入「精華區」，於是比我貼返出黎比大家觀摩，唔洗兩日GP都爆埋，阿豪嘅巴哈小屋比人圍，之前阿豪講好會係今個星期上巴哈節目討論劇情結果失蹤，龜縮成個星期之後今日編輯部主管出黎道歉，但其實都係一篇廢話，結論係阿豪想辭職但係獲巴哈編輯部挽留，同南華一樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/05/195932_5587db0cde5a5153fb73ebf97a88b125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F05%2F195932_5587db0cde5a5153fb73ebf97a88b125.jpg&h=cbec6e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢個毫無誠嘅道歉post邊會有人受，秒速破百BP被摺疊，所以花生仲有排食，等緊豪哥上水的一天"},{"pid":"23b654a580385a7c03bf1bba9af2d45de7477f00","tid":2077665,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"巴哈編輯部主管道歉post:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=21876&amp;snA=2729&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D21876%26snA%3D2729%26tnum%3D1&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmE7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=36db1544\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=21876&amp;snA=2729&amp;tnum=1</a>"},{"pid":"df4dd21382f54c218e839ec339b